  <h2>Soil Moisture Monitor</h2>
  <p>The Soil Moisture Monitor is a device designed for monitoring soil moisture levels to support optimal plant care. Built on the Sensor View Template, it provides real-time data without triggering automated irrigation.</p>

  <div><img src="/assets/img/soil-moisture-monitor.webp" alt="Soil Moisture Monitor"></div>

  <h3>Template</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/templates/sensor-view">Sensor View</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Key Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Heavy duty waterproof sensor</li>
    <li>Continuous soil moisture monitoring</li>
    <li>Non-irrigating sensor setup</li>
    <li>Displays the current soil moisture reading.</li>
    <li>Buttons to calibrate the sensor.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Use Cases</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Greenhouse Monitoring</li>
    <li>Home Plant Care</li>
  </ul>

